title: Inside Mrs. Fields founder's former ranch listed for $45 million
text:
Inside Mrs. Fields founder's former ranch listed for $45 million

10:55 AM ET Sat, 14 Sept 2019

To view this site, you need to have JavaScript enabled in your browser, and either the Flash Plugin or an HTML5-Video enabled browser. Download the latest Flash player and try again.

The $.45 million ranch that Debbie Fields, founder of Mrs. Fields' Cookies, built is for sale See all the details of the 17,000-square-foot main home, two smaller homes, and the rest of the property the cookie mogul created.
